												<img width="100" height="100" src="https://www.dailysignal.com/wp-content/uploads/Michelle-Obama-100x100.jpg" class="attachment-square_medium size-square_medium wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://www.dailysignal.com/wp-content/uploads/Michelle-Obama-100x100.jpg 100w, https://www.dailysignal.com/wp-content/uploads/Michelle-Obama-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.dailysignal.com/wp-content/uploads/Michelle-Obama-50x50.jpg 50w, https://www.dailysignal.com/wp-content/uploads/Michelle-Obama-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.dailysignal.com/wp-content/uploads/Michelle-Obama-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.dailysignal.com/wp-content/uploads/Michelle-Obama-550x550.jpg 550w, https://www.dailysignal.com/wp-content/uploads/Michelle-Obama-470x470.jpg 470w" sizes="(max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px" />					</a>
					<h2>
						<a href="https://www.dailysignal.com/2020/04/14/the-left-is-calling-for-mail-in-voting-heres-why-its-a-bad-idea/" class="ga-event" data-ga-event-details='{"category": "Article Discovery", "action": "Must Reads", "label": "Article 3"}'>The Left Is Calling for Mail-In Voting. Here’s Why It’s a Bad Idea.</a>
					</h2>
